  "text": "Ussing chamber studies. During days 15-29, transepithelial electrical characteristics and Si transport were measured. The tissues were supported by 150-m nylon mesh and mounted in Ussing chambers as previously described [CITATION_1] . The temperature was maintained at 39°C, and the saline bathing the luminal and basolateral sides of the tissue was continuously gassed (95% O 2-5% CO2) and stirred throughout the experiment.",
